{"tid":992092,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"做負重用唔同器材 做既重量都會唔同？","createTime":"2019-01-23T01:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T08:59:35.000Z","uid":222678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5a15134fb0ecec7ea6a0e77746319be9eb51ad","tid":992092,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"話說我做開20kg啞鈴臥推 左20kg 右20kg咁樣<br />\n動作係呢隻<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aQv5wB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aQv5wB.png&h=68bb1c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係唔知做咩事 間gym啞鈴20kg冇左一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到做唔到 走左去做史密斯機<br />\n呢隻：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqHN7Lj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqHN7Lj.png&h=84909d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇 明明我做開啞鈴兩個加埋40kg<br />\n轉左個部機之後 只可以做到total 20-25kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪正常？我有諗過係咪條bar重量影響<br />\n但係條bar點重都唔會有20kg掛？"},{"pid":"9a6fd354111fb1e9595d556900edfb67441bb591","tid":992092,"uid":17275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"Smith machine支bar 間間都唔同wor<br />\n都around 20lbs<br />\n<br />\n加上兩個動作唔同<br />\n你可能未適應"},{"pid":"0393e67bec35fca31b36cdd7356a3868a14cd252","tid":992092,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a6fd354111fb1e9595d556900edfb67441bb591","tid":992092,"uid":17275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"Smith machine支bar 間間都唔同wor<br />\n都around 20lbs<br />\n<br />\n加上兩個動作唔同<br />\n你可能未適應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:57:11.000Z","msg":"練biceps 又係咁 拎dumbbells 做開10kg 左10右10<br />\n用EZ-bar做 做得10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  廿其實咁樣影唔影響增肌？"},{"pid":"e37cb4bfe1510a7186d90ab5a40ac7ec25345269","tid":992092,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:02:24.000Z","msg":"唔同器材當然會唔同重量<br />\n就係有些微角度分別, 都會影響你習慣用開果舊肌肉<br />\n令你做唔番一貫個重量<br />\n所以成日都叫人做開一種動作就轉另一種."},{"pid":"689738c53cd78638a2238562a8e53ddcb185c4ee","tid":992092,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:11:52.000Z","msg":"根本佢兩個都唔係同一個動作黎 用既肌肉都唔同 最緊要既唔係重量 係你肌肉既感受程度同動作姿勢正唔正確 千其唔好ego lifting 做重無獎拎 傷左就一世"},{"pid":"6189b70f8d9c00f53cc7672080731b9bc0ee66c8","tid":992092,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a51bf211bf4ed8144d4565efa6f0182e2795051b","tid":992092,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"做機唔使用微肌肉平衡輕好多"},{"pid":"3c6db4fe31f72add56b7fa78c429ed6eea55fd4a","tid":992092,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"其實做機同啞鈴橫鈴有咩好壞處"},{"pid":"50f430fd67b4df0792fe72347657e5ba363ae0d4","tid":992092,"uid":186272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6189b70f8d9c00f53cc7672080731b9bc0ee66c8","tid":992092,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"Smith有鋼繩釣住<br />\n輕好多"},{"pid":"178af349cc43b27043fa25b7948721ccacd28000","tid":992092,"uid":130421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"同你有同一樣既問題 <br />\n做左幾個禮拜史密夫都係做唔到重 要輕5到10磅先做到 <br />\n因為以前做開啞鈴<br />\n而家有時做返我12reps 每邊40磅feel唔到胸肌發力 姿勢唔好做返30磅到姿勢先正確<br />\n史密夫又推唔重 推啞鈴力量又低左 好迷惘"}]}